  "title": "RPM Ep. 56 | The case for emerging managers with Ted Panarese and Aditya Fontana-Raina",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2026-03-12T19:42:46+00:00\" title=\"Thursday, March 12, 2026 - 19:42\">Thu, 03/12/2026 - 19:42</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">RPM Ep. 56 | The case for emerging managers with Ted Panarese and Aditya Fontana-Raina</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"StepstoneFeatured\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/StepstoneFeatured.jpg\" height=\"422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/StepstoneFeatured.jpg\" width=\"1004\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>In this episode of RPM, Ted Panarese and Aditya Fontana-Raina, New York-based Partners on our private equity team, join co-host Anna Marcus to explore whether emerging managers truly represent a disproportionate source of risk, or if the opportunity has been mischaracterized. They cover:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e6df63f480a8ad835d92dce3c09bff766\">Revisiting the case for emerging managers (3:02)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e57a548e3b3ec6bf4c315a46591783d50\">What the data says about early-fund outperformance (4:12)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9e8d786c27fec45ab72147f84e3a238d\">The ideal Fund I profile (6:41)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e59a4acb9ab8acd3eab6e05477c5b1678\">Risks with Fund I investing (11:15)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eba846d15cafb0c1a6ff637648d0cf898\">Building a disciplined emerging manager playbook (13:52)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e96c8c9373c833e223aa8d579c1621521\">How LPs should underwrite risk at the program and portfolio level (16:36)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e51cf6229c65025b10652bb9ee2e3bd5f\">Key takeaways (21:32)</li></ul><p></p><p>Read the transcript .</p><p>RPM is available on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/rpm-reflections-on-private-markets/id1537055419\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/1xZBHwyP2Bx6RRkMJKXOaP\">Spotify</a>—anywhere you normally get your podcasts. Subscribe today! </p><p><a class=\"btn btn-tritory\" href=\"https://insuranceaum.com/stepstone\">READ MORE FROM STEPSTONE GROUP</a></p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/de